  "text": "We implemented a counting algorithm proposed by [CITATION_1] on a swarm of physical e-puck robots and expanded it to also include a role assignment mechanism. The algorithm could be easily adapted for different platforms. The only requirements are that the robots have local communication, memory to store the lists and an interface to interact with the operator.",
